{"id":"iron-steel-supplement-prebuilts","name":"Iron & Steel \u2014 Supplement Pre-Builts","version":"1.0","publisher":"DiceForge Studios Ltd.","description":"3 vehicles \u2014 Iron & Steel \u2014 Supplement Pre-Builts","weapons":[],"mods":[],"specials":[],"vehicles":[{"name":"M4A3 Sherman (Easy Eight)","desc":"America's workhorse tank with the improved high-velocity gun. She can finally hurt a Panther from the front, which is all her crews ever asked for.","notes":"Pre-built Sherman for immediate play. The baseline Allied tank for any WWII Western Front scenario.","image":"","size":8,"loco":"tracked","mods":{},"weapons":[{"weaponId":"tank_gun_med","mount":"turret","linked":0},{"weaponId":"slug_med","mount":"fixed","linked":0},{"weaponId":"hmg","mount":"pintle","linked":0}],"toughLevel":0,"armourLevel":0,"speedLevel":0,"handlingLevel":0,"woundsLevel":0},{"name":"Tiger I","desc":"Eighty-eight millimetres of fear. She kills at two kilometres and her reputation precedes her by ten.","notes":"Pre-built Tiger for immediate deployment as a boss encounter. Every Allied player should dread seeing one.","image":"","size":8,"loco":"tracked","mods":{},"weapons":[{"weaponId":"tank_gun_heavy","mount":"turret","linked":0},{"weaponId":"slug_med","mount":"fixed","linked":0}],"toughLevel":1,"armourLevel":2,"speedLevel":-1,"handlingLevel":-1,"woundsLevel":0,"mphOverride":28},{"name":"T-34/85","desc":"The improved T-34 with a bigger turret and an 85mm gun that finally matches the Panzer IV. She wins through numbers and reliability.","notes":"Pre-built T-34 for immediate play in Eastern Front scenarios. The definitive Soviet medium tank.","image":"","size":7,"loco":"tracked","mods":{"sloped_armour":1},"weapons":[{"weaponId":"tank_gun_med","mount":"turret","linked":0},{"weaponId":"slug_med","mount":"fixed","linked":0}],"toughLevel":0,"armourLevel":1,"speedLevel":0,"handlingLevel":0,"woundsLevel":0,"crewLevel":3}]}